channel.title: Hybridscape, starting from level 1
channel.description:
Okay, I realize Hybridscape is NOT a public server so all you angry MoparScape fools don't come herding to my topic to be absolutely rude. That's to start.
Now for those who make it past that, all I simply want to know is how can I start a level 1 in Hybridscape. I've changed my character files but when I do and try to log on it always says "You are already logged on" or something of the sort. I know this is probably a simple question, though believe me when I say I've searched around with no results. Hence the "impossible" part lol.
By level 1 i mean level 1 in everything.. and not a gm. I personally don't find it fun to start at 99 in everything.
Thank you for your time, and I appreciate any help.
